PRICED TO SELL !! Seller has UPDATED both bathrooms, NEW carpet , freshly painted the home & Additional BONUS - SOLAR PANELS ARE INCLUDED WITH NO ADDITONAL COST.!! 
Welcome to your new home . This charming pre- loved  3 bed, 2 bath offers the perfect blend of updates without losing charm, making it an ideal haven for your family. Step inside  be impressed by the newly installed carpet, updated light fixtures, fresh paint throughout with  fully updated master bathroom. Tile flooring flows throughout the home with warming carpet in the bedrooms. Step into the bright  airy living room enhanced by Cathedral ceilings and a timeless brick fireplace. Never miss a moment with family and friends in the open kitchen and separate dining room. Stretch out in the spacious owner's suite with large walk-in closet, as well as roomy minor bedrooms. Added bonus: 16X10 shed in the backyard for extra storage of lawn equipment and more! Convenience is key with this location - just minutes from schools and a short drive to Fort Cavasos for our military service members. Call todayfor your private tour.
